Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  Angelic Howl Ⅰ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:29.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}世界の影にいたけど聞こえたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:35.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}寂しい　悲しい夜の　遠吠え
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:40.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}薄い毛布を貫く声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:44.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}肌に傷をつける
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:52.16,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}あなたが落とした目印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:20:01.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}辿って歩けば　明かりが森の中浮かぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:06.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}ドアを開けていいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:12.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}「キミのこと救える」なんて嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}切なくなるからやめてね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:22.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}これ以上は泣きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:27.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}それでも信じたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:28.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}MY HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:33.96,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}心は壊れている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:40.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}それでも　愛して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:29.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}無論你身處天涯海角我都能聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:35.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}回響在這寂寞悲傷之夜的哭喊聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:40.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}穿透裹在你身的毛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:44.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}刺痛著我每一寸肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:52.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}你所遺落下來的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:20:01.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}追尋著它的痕跡  森林中的一縷亮光映入眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:06.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}能否打開這扇封閉的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:12.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}「我一定能拯救你」之類的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}只會徒增傷心  請別輕易說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:22.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}不想再變得更傷心欲絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:27.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}內心卻讓我去相信這份承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:28.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}MY HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:33.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}我的心已分崩離碎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:40.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}但這海誓山盟卻不會變
